flow.name: ContractApproval
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions targetNamespace="point.io" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
  <message name="point.io:testquick" id="testquick"/>
  <process isExecutable="true" name="ContractApproval" id="ContractApproval">
    <documentation>review and approve documents</documentation>
    <startEvent name="Start Review" id="start"/>
    <userTask activiti:assignee="${ContractAdmin}" name="Assign Approver for Contract: ${contractName}" id="addParties">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:formProperty type="enum" name="Party 1 Role" id="party1_role">
          <activiti:value name="Approver" id="Approver"/>
          <activiti:value name="Respondee" id="Respondee"/>
        </activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty type="string" name="Party 1 Email" id="party1_email"/>
        <activiti:formProperty type="enum" name="Party 2 Role" id="party2_role">
          <activiti:value name="Approver" id="Approver"/>
          <activiti:value name="Respondee" id="Respondee"/>
        </activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty type="string" name="Party 2 Email" id="party2_email"/>
        <activiti:formProperty type="enum" name="Party 3 Role" id="party3_role">
          <activiti:value name="Approver" id="Approver"/>
          <activiti:value name="Respondee" id="Respondee"/>
        </activiti:formProperty>
        <activiti:formProperty type="string" name="Party 3 Email" id="party3_email"/>
        <activiti:formProperty required="true" type="enum" name="Option Selection" id="wf_optionsOutcome">
          <activiti:value name="Continue" id="continue"/>
          <activiti:value name="Add More Parties" id="addmore"/>
          <activiti:value name="Cancel" id="cancel"/>
        </activiti:formProperty>
      </extensionElements>
    </userTask>
    <endEvent name="End Review" id="end"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.wf_Add_Parties" name="Set Parties Manual" id="addPartyServiceTask"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="addPartyServiceTask" sourceRef="addParties" id="flow28"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="addParties" sourceRef="addPartyServiceTask" id="flow30">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == "addmore"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="end" sourceRef="addPartyServiceTask" id="flow31">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == "cancel"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <subProcess name="ApproveReject" id="ApproveReject">
      <multiInstanceLoopCharacteristics activiti:elementVariable="assignee" activiti:collection="Approver_LIST_COL" isSequential="false"/>
      <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_review_formid" activiti:assignee="${assignee}" name="Review & Approve Contract: ${contractName}" id="review">
        <documentation>Review associated documents and Approve/Reject.</documentation>
      </userTask>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="reviewDecision" sourceRef="review" id="flow27">
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:executionListener class="plugins.SnapShot" event="take">
            <activiti:field name="recordType">
              <activiti:string>ReviewSubmitted</activiti:string>
            </activiti:field>
          </activiti:executionListener>
        </extensionElements>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <exclusiveGateway id="reviewDecision"/>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="usertask1" sourceRef="reviewDecision" id="flowapprove">
        <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == "approve"}</conditionExpression>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="reviewUpdate" sourceRef="reviewDecision" id="flowreject">
        <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == "requestChange"}</conditionExpression>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_update_formid" activiti:assignee="${ContractAdmin}" name="Updates Requested for Contract: ${contractName}" id="reviewUpdate">
        <documentation>Select reason for Rejection.</documentation>
      </userTask>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="exclusivegateway1" sourceRef="reviewUpdate" id="flow14"/>
      <serviceTask activiti:type="mail" name="Rejected Mail" id="rejectMail">
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:field name="to">
            <activiti:expression>${ContractAdmin}</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="from">
            <activiti:string>alert@point.io</activiti:string>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="subject">
            <activiti:expression>Request update ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} Rejected</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="html">
            <activiti:expression>Your request id ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} has been reviewed and rejected by ${assignee}.</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
        </extensionElements>
      </serviceTask>
      <exclusiveGateway name="Detail Required?" id="exclusivegateway1"/>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="rejectMail" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" id="flowother">
        <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == 'cancel'}</conditionExpression>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="scripttask1" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" id="flowstd">
        <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == 'resend'}</conditionExpression>
      </sequenceFlow>
      <endEvent name="End SubFlow Review" id="endevent1"/>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="rejectMail" id="flow40"/>
      <startEvent name="Start SubFlow Review" id="startevent1"/>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="scripttask2" sourceRef="startevent1" id="flow45"/>
      <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_approve_formid" activiti:assignee="${ContractAdmin}" name="Final Approval Contract: ${contractName}" id="usertask1"/>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="approveMail" sourceRef="usertask1" id="flow47"/>
      <scriptTask activiti:autoStoreVariables="false" scriptFormat="javascript" name="update approved" id="scripttask1">
        <script>testvar = "test value";
</script>
      </scriptTask>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="review" sourceRef="scripttask1" id="flow49"/>
      <scriptTask activiti:autoStoreVariables="false" scriptFormat="javascript" name="task Settings" id="scripttask2">
        <script>
execution.setVariableLocal("approvedBy", execution.getVariableLocal(assignee));
execution.setVariableLocal("updateRequestedBy", execution.getVariableLocal(assignee));

</script>
      </scriptTask>
      <serviceTask activiti:type="mail" name="Approved Mail" id="approveMail">
        <extensionElements>
          <activiti:field name="to">
            <activiti:expression>${assignee}</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="from">
            <activiti:string>alert@point.io</activiti:string>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="subject">
            <activiti:string>Contract has been Approved!</activiti:string>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="html">
            <activiti:expression>Contract Approval with id: ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} has been reviewed and approved by ${assignee} and ${ContractAdmin}</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
          <activiti:field name="cc">
            <activiti:expression>${ContractAdmin}</activiti:expression>
          </activiti:field>
        </extensionElements>
      </serviceTask>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="approveMail" id="flow39"/>
      <sequenceFlow targetRef="review" sourceRef="scripttask2" id="flow50"/>
    </subProcess>
    <serviceTask activiti:type="mail" name="Notify Final" id="mailtask1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="to">
          <activiti:expression>${Respondee_LIST}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="from">
          <activiti:string>alert@point.io</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="subject">
          <activiti:expression>You are being notified that the Process ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} has completed.</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="html">
          <activiti:expression><p>Process ${execution.getProcessInstanceId()} started by ${Originator_LIST} has completed.</p>
<p>
<table>
<tr><td>Approvers:</td><td>${Approver_LIST}</td></tr>
<tr><td>CC:</td><td>${Originator_LIST}</td></tr>
</table>
</p></activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="cc">
          <activiti:expression>${Originator_LIST}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="end" sourceRef="mailtask1" id="flow26"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="ApproveReject" sourceRef="addPartyServiceTask" id="flow38"/>
    <inclusiveGateway name="Inclusive Gateway" id="inclusivegateway1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="inclusivegateway1" sourceRef="ApproveReject" id="flow41"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="mailtask1" sourceRef="inclusivegateway1" id="flow42"/>
    <scriptTask activiti:autoStoreVariables="false" scriptFormat="javascript" name="initial Settings" id="initialSettings">
      <script>
if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_review_formid")) execution.setVariable("poi_review_formid", "552f699c1a0000e80d1571b1");
if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_update_formid")) execution.setVariable("poi_update_formid", "552f69d61a0000ec0d1571b3");
if (null == execution.getVariable("poi_approve_formid")) execution.setVariable("poi_approve_formid", "552f69eb1a0000ed0d1571b5");
if (null == execution.getVariable("ContractAdmin")) execution.setVariable("ContractAdmin", "jwang@point.io");

if (null == execution.getVariable("contractName")) execution.setVariable("contractName", " ");



modify_Comments="THIS MUTUAL NON-DISCLOSURE AGREEMENT (\"Agreement\") is entered into between Comcast Inc., with offices at Comcast Center, 1701 JFK Boulevard, Philadelphia, PA 19103, on behalf of itself and for the benefit of its Affiliates, hereinafter defined (individually or collectively \"Comcast\") and Point.io (\"Company\"), with offices at 3401 Market Street, Philadelphia, PA 19104 as of the 17th day of April, 2015 (\"Effective Date\"). Comcast and Company may be referred to herein individually as a \"Party\" and collectively as the \"Parties.\"\n11.  This Agreement will terminate two (2) years after the Effective Date, or may be terminated by either Party at any time upon thirty (30) days written notice to the other Party.  Each Partyâs obligations under this Agreement will survive termination of this Agreement, continue indefinitely and will be binding upon such Partyâs heirs, successors, and permitted assigns. ";

execution.setVariable("modify_Comments", modify_Comments);
</script>
    </scriptTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="addParties" sourceRef="initialSettings" id="flow48"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="initialSettings" sourceRef="start" id="flow51"/>
  </process>
